description:
Hi there this is the cristmass obby from 2023. Drag objects to make your way in this obby. 
 
 until Christmas you can each day play a new level. you can collect coins. Collect them all to buy a gift at the end from the Obby. What give you a random badge for a decoration in a new game release next year. 
 
 Hold on my socials or take a look in my group for information about when it realase is. 
 
 Buy the tool pass to get a speed coil and a gravity coil 
 
 Premium users will get a Benefit in new year obby if they complete the obby 
 
 Note: deu a bug on the tutorial prompts by the level signs (Seizure Warning: A loading bug may cause rapid flashing images when using some prompts. Individuals with photosensitive epilepsy should use caution.)
